          "reviewTitle": "Great Coverage Without Looking Heavy!",
          "reviewText": "Why did I wait so long. Great coverage. Love it. Color match was easy and on point! A lot of product for the money. Will buy again.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 28, 2026",
          "customer": "Amazon Customer",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHRETKFYITWJOCPWCAIIQK5EIBVQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "size": "3.3 Fl Oz (Pack of 1)",
            "color": "Light"
          }
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "This is a good one!",
          "reviewText": "I\u2019m enjoying this makeup. Coverage is light so it doesn\u2019t look like I\u2019m wearing foundation. It helps even out my complexion for daytime wear. For more coverage, add more layers. Easy to apply and blends easily over my moisturizer. Though it\u2019s not necessary, a large makeup brush blends it all over better than my fingers and without stretching the skin. What I especially love is that it doesn\u2019t have that reflective appearance that most foundations seem to have these days. Doesn\u2019t make my little skin bumps stand out more. I bought two shades. They are darker than I expected but one gives me a tanned look. The Medium is still a bit darker than I might need, but again, it blends really well and my little dark spots show less. Haven\u2019t tried it on my legs yet, but if I ever decide to, I feel confident it\u2019ll look good. Added perk, the ingredients used are said to be healthy. Seems a great value all around!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on August 21, 2025",
          "customer": "M. Powell",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AGPJVCMGG3LCG2XAM6OWC4GBUVDA",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "size": "3.3 Fl Oz (Pack of 1)",
            "color": "Medium"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "7 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Transfer resistent",
          "reviewText": "This is better than their dark blue tube ...Body Perfector...it doesn't cake so bad and rub off so easily....none of these products on the market are that great...but this one seems better than most.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2026",
          "customer": "Aurora Guarino",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AFABE2KZZ25RCGD44G6NP6AFTQLQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 4,
